name: CircularFifoQueue_elementTest
description: Unit tests for the element method of CircularFifoQueue.

test_cases.name: testElementWhenQueueIsEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of the element method when the queue is empty, expecting a NoSuchElementException.

test_cases.name: testElementWhenQueueHasOneElement
test_cases.description: Tests the element method when the queue has one element, expecting the element to be returned.

test_cases.name: testElementWhenQueueIsFull
test_cases.description: Tests the element method when the queue is full, expecting the first element to be returned.

test_cases.name: testElementAfterRemovingElement
test_cases.description: Tests the element method after removing an element from the queue, expecting the next element to be returned.

test_cases.name: testElementAfterAddingAndRemovingElements
test_cases.description: Tests the element method after adding and removing elements from the queue, expecting the correct element to be returned.
